'''Mathilde''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of a nation-state of the same name on [[Renatasia III]]. The nation-state of Mathilde was located on Renatasia's second largest continent, in the northern temperate zone of the planet.

Mathilde's primary output was divided equally between agriculture and manufacturing.

